  "text": "Seedlings were used for DNA purification and genotyped for the relevant T-DNA [CITATION_1] with wild-type and insertion-specific PCR products. Many green seeds and some apparently normal seed produced by the AGL90 heterozygous seed parent failed to germinate.",
